VARIABLES

PLAYBOOK
- hosts: websrvgrp
  vars:
    http_port: 80
    sqluser: admin

-------

Inventory based

In inventory file
group_vars/all
group_vars/groupname
host_vars/hostname

-------

Roles

Include variables from files in playbook

--------

Fact variables: Setup module

ansible_os_family = Os name like RedHat, Debian etc

ansible_processor_cores = Number of CPU cores

ansible_kernel = Kernel version

ansible_devices = Connection Device informay=tion

ansible_default_ipv4 = IP,MAC address, gateway etc

ansible_architecture = 64 bit or 32 bit
---------

Store Output: register module

Module Execution(Play Tasks) > Return Output(Json format) > Store Output(Variable to store) > Use Variable(In Tasks/Print it)